beware of christians is a 2010 american documentary film . it is directed by will bakke , produced by michael b. allen and alex carroll , and stars michael b. allen , will bakke , alex carroll , and matt owen . this is will bakke 's second documentary film . original production began in april 2009 in dallas , texas and completed in april 2010 . the film has had limited screening around the us since it premiered on april 3 , 2010 , and was released on dvd january 14 , 2011 . the film is notable for its controversial title and unique distribution model of " &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; " .